{"tid":1286584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想遍地開花，係要當地民眾自發，唔係叫你去幫","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:08:11.000Z","uid":64191,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"848461357a0c8c19c3850eceebe2bc13e90a44e1","tid":1286584,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"歐洲18世紀民族革命、近代東歐革命、幾年前既阿拉伯之春，全部都係由當地民眾自覺發起，而唔係由A地人幫B地人<br />\n<br />\n只係剛好大家有共同覺悟，先會一石激起千層浪，好喇，而家香港反送中抗爭，係為對抗中國魔掌伸入香港既司法、經濟等自主權，可以話係憲制保衛戰<br />\n<br />\n但武漢今次僅係環保抗爭，甚至之前廣東等地亦然，訊息封鎖下佢地冇反中央政府既心，而家亦只係要Make Noise<br />\n<br />\n更何況，香港仲被人入緊七粒，一個目標都未達成，就想分兵幫忙？開太多戰線係自殺, Understand? 專心落自己既目標<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲有大把抗爭方式要自己學習、研究"},{"pid":"920ecd502d07565f6a1a746019d46b2d07ec64f1","tid":1286584,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ff06e91899993272eb9e51bd208a8d5470b6439","tid":1286584,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"See? Focus黎緊兩日既九龍新界戰線啦"},{"pid":"8bfe0c2b49bb4fd741ea563394949dfdaa23b168","tid":1286584,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"推 搞好香港呢邊，引起更多人關注，促使當地民眾自發就足夠<br />\n<br />\n我無野講"}]}